Title: Surface Bound
Description:
$n, the moment is upon us. We must make haste to the city of Dornogal, where our allies await. 

Only together do we stand a chance against Harbinger's machinations.
ObjectivesText: Meet with Moira Thaurissan and your allies in Dornogal in the Isle of Dorn.

Objectives.Text: Meet with Moira Thaurissan in Dornogal
